CHIP HOPE CO LTD (8084)  said unconsolidated sales
in May rose 0.85% to NT$278,487,000 from NT$276,152,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            278,487          276,152    
YOY%              0.85%    -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,007,070        1,240,754   
YOY%             -18.83% 
=================================================================
 